  <abstract>Image of a police man and a woman standing in front of the Toronto Dominion Tower. A sign at entrance of the tower says &apos;With this beam.&apos; Another sign is at the forefront in between the woman and the police man which says &apos;Do you want your signature preserved for posterity in the Commonwealth&apos;s tallest building? Sign anywhere on the beam with an ordinary lead pencil.&quot;</abstract>
